{"tid":588267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真相大白 普京否認曾裸上身騎熊 「我認真工作的照片沒人想看」","createTime":"2018-03-11T05:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T13:42:55.000Z","uid":3393,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"50bb6a1ce4566776b342eca7216ba2154415d290","tid":588267,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/167069/thumbnail/d562bcd6cb5920fcdaca1957ba13e69f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F167069%2Fthumbnail%2Fd562bcd6cb5920fcdaca1957ba13e69f.jpg&h=1ffd6dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n普京本月初接受美國國家廣播公司（NBC）時，記者凱利（Megyn Kelly）問及普京有這麼多裸上身的照片，他的回應不失幽默，亦同時表示網上熱傳的「普京騎熊圖」是完全虛構的。<br />\n<br />\n凱利先問普京，「作為總統，投射力量有多重要？」普京回應說，「投射不重要，顯露力量才重要。」凱利接着道：「為何我這麼問，是因為在美國，經常會見到你祼着上身騎馬的照片。」普京聽完後隨即微笑起來，回道：「那時我正在休假。那是你俄羅斯的同業，那是互聯網。但我們並非刻意這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n普京續稱：「他們拍一些他們想拍的照片。我也有很多我工作時、處理文件的照片，但沒有人想看。」凱利笑着指：「你意指他們很喜歡你裸着上身？」<br />\n<br />\n普京笑着回應：「你知道嗎？我看過我騎熊的照片，但我從來沒有騎過。但這樣的圖像確實存在。」<br />\n<br />\n現年65歲的普京的熱愛戶外活動,，保養得宜，常毫不吝嗇展現健壯身材，媒體經常拍得他赤膊上身的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1267336/xlarge/61a40fbcc8673be9b53bc6bfff5d4950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1267336%2Fxlarge%2F61a40fbcc8673be9b53bc6bfff5d4950.jpg&h=247efc4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1267358/xlarge/f404f8b0b87074272bd35969ad13bebb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1267358%2Fxlarge%2Ff404f8b0b87074272bd35969ad13bebb.jpg&h=393c26e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1267370/xlarge/5c32139642bcc959d3349b749d8747ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1267370%2Fxlarge%2F5c32139642bcc959d3349b749d8747ef.jpg&h=187374fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1267362/xlarge/984a9867c67b6abdabd131985875dfdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1267362%2Fxlarge%2F984a9867c67b6abdabd131985875dfdc.jpg&h=59f24496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1267372/xlarge/285adb1995574cfa2f232c8da488031a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1267372%2Fxlarge%2F285adb1995574cfa2f232c8da488031a.jpg&h=4fbace8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/國際/167069/真相大白-普京否認曾裸上身騎熊-我認真工作的照片沒人想看-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F167069%2F%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E5%A4%A7%E7%99%BD-%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%9B%BE%E8%A3%B8%E4%B8%8A%E8%BA%AB%E9%A8%8E%E7%86%8A-%E6%88%91%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E6%B2%92%E4%BA%BA%E6%83%B3%E7%9C%8B-&d=wnrB4YlbdlhvLVZtTTAyVMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=a5d51a92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/國際/167069/真相大白-普京否認曾裸上身騎熊-我認真工作的照片沒人想看-</a>"},{"pid":"47ea10e8809fd883eba1b0784c489ecf92bbfc9f","tid":588267,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08b515dde924e630d5c4727ad1b9edfdc4108f2","tid":588267,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:51:40.000Z","msg":"香港人係狗"},{"pid":"6e2cc7092ec6a2f0fef2dff9858499e1aa69c077","tid":588267,"uid":34461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"一個軍人嘅樣"},{"pid":"1dccc3dce7b0174caaae3d3635d8f7621b717b8f","tid":588267,"uid":22422,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/140340_3a349a1cd8a36ec01286dd3f03167987.png\